---
title: "Orthomodularity and the incompatibility of Relativity and Quantum mechanics"
collection: publications
permalink: '/publications/Orthomodularity-and-the-incompatibility-of-relativity-and-quantum-mechanics'
excerpt: "We show that orthomodularity in general and non-existence of isotropic vectors in particular decisively yield the geometry of quantum mechanics and that a fundamental reason why quantum mechanics and relativity cannot be unified is because of the non-existence of isotropic vectors"
date: 2016-10-25
venue: 'Quaid-i-Azam University'
paperurl: 'https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40509-016-0092-8'
---
